Ebon Moss-Bachrach https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ebon_Moss-Bachrach 0 Ebon Moss-Bachrach (born March 19, 1977) is an American actor best known for playing the role of David Lieberman in The Punisher and Niels Sørensen in The Last Ship.
